data.description: Welcome to your future home in Ault, CO! This charming townhome, built in 2021, boasts 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a heated two-car garage-perfect for those chilly Colorado winters. Enjoy modern living with stainless steel appliances included in the contemporary kitchen, complete with a convenient island for meal prep. Need extra space? You'll love the loft bonus area! Plus, separate laundry room with washer and dryer included for added convenience. Outside, a fenced front yard offers a cozy outdoor space, while being within walking distance to schools and a neighborhood park provides convenience and community vibes. Don't miss out on this gem!
